   --- Third-party data ---

   The `datasets/` directory mirrors identifier lists and derived
   overlap counts from the following upstream sources under their
   respective licenses:

     * DeepDTA (Öztürk et al., 2018)  — MIT license, repo at hkmztrk/DeepDTA
     * Struct2Graph (Baranwal et al., 2022) — MIT-equivalent, repo at baranwa2/Struct2Graph
     * OnionNet (Zheng et al., 2019)  — MIT license, repo at zhenglz/onionnet
     * HAC-Net (Kyro et al., 2023)    — per gregory-kyro/HAC-Net
     * MVSO-PPIS (et al., 2025)       — per Edwardblue282/MVSO-PPIS
     * TEFDTA (et al., 2024)          — per RefDawn-XD/TEFDTA
     * HGRL-DTA (et al., 2022)        — per Zhaoyang-Chu/HGRL-DTA
     * DCGAN-DTA (et al., 2024)       — per mojtabaze7/DCGAN-DTA
     * MGraphDTA (et al., 2022)       — per guaguabujianle/MGraphDTA
     * AttentionDTA (Zhao et al.)     — per zhaoqichang/AttentionDTA_TCBB
     * RaPPPID (Szymborski 2022)      — Internet Archive mirror (pointer only)

   We mirror only the IDENTIFIER LISTS required to reproduce the
   manuscript's overlap analyses. The LICENSED PAYLOADS (PDBbind
   affinity values, ChEMBL property tables, BindingDB Ki data) are
   referenced by ID only and must be obtained from their original
   publishers under their own license terms.
